CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: InnovAge Holding Corp is a healthcare delivery platform by several participants focused on providing all-inclusive, capitated care to high-cost, dual-eligible seniors. Its patient-centered care delivery approach improves the quality of care while keeping them in their homes and reducing over-utilization of high-cost care settings such as hospitals and nursing homes. The company's segment includes PACE and others. It generates maximum revenue from the PACE segment.
